
Requirement: build an inventory management system include below features:
-          Save the status and location of hardware unit in the warehouse: type, model, serial number, import date, location in warehouse, status, owner (who is borrowing/using this device)

-          Client can connect to server to query device info

-          Administrator can connect to server to query/add/update/delete device info

-          Server allow maximum 5 connections in a meantime


Platform: Windows 10 (64bits)
Programming language: Python


Platform: Windows 10 (64bits), control via either console or GUI
Database: there is no special requirement for DB
Programming language: Python (2.7.12)
    third-party : tabulate

